 MUSIC fans will be in for a treat tonight as the crème de la crème of entertainers share the stage online courtesy of ZB Bank. The list of performers includes Jah Prayzah, Janet Manyowa, Takura, Tamy Moyo, Tocky Vibes, Poptain and Allanah. Dubbed Something Big Is Brewing, the event will be held on Facebook starting at 1800hours.
The award-winning musician recently launched her latest single Tariro which is performing well on the market.      — LIFESTYLE WRITER